</XX>
<CN>FRZ  France, EC.
    SEZ  Sweden, West Europe.
    XGZ  Europe.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P3711 Motor Vehicles and Car Bodies.
    P3714 Motor Vehicle Parts and Accessories.
    P6231 Security and Commodity Exchanges.
</IN>
