<TEXT>
CASINO, one of France's largest food retailing groups, achieved a three-fold
increase in pre-tax profits to FFr60.1m (Dollars 10.32m) in the first half
of the year, writes John Ridding in Paris.
The rise from FFr18m in the first six months of 1992 reflected its merger
